Body:
Description: When logging in, it is displayed that the password has expired. When changing the password, the current password is not accepted. Message: "The password provided ist different from the existing password".

The password is copied and pasted into the corresponding field.

Steps to Reproduce Updated: 2025.05.20: 
Log in with the user.
The UI asks to set a new password.
The password is copied and pasted into the corresponding field.
The password does not save.
Next Steps Updated: 2025.05.20: Proposed a remote connection with the customer.
What We've Learned Updated: 2025.05.20: The user can't set the new password.
